      <h3>üìê Devine la nature de l'angle !</h3>
      <style>
        .quiz-container {
          border: 2px solid #f39c12;
          border-radius: 12px;
          padding: 1rem;
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          background: #fff3c4;
          max-width: 600px;
